\[\lambda_{D}(\Gamma^{*})\leq\lambda_{D}(\Gamma^{*}+P)\leq\lambda_{D}(\Gamma^{*})+ \frac{\eta_{0}^{2}\gamma^{2}}{ND}\|w_{*}\|^{2}.\]

